name: Natalia
description:
I have work, I am intelligent, educated and loving person. Telling really I can say that I have almost everything, I just was not able to find the one who can be called the soulmate for me, the one who really loves me.
I search for the reliable and loving person. Which ready to serious relationship. Ready to turn a life to the best party. For this purpose it is necessary to be assured and resolute, and also risky and strong spirit. I wish to find the person with whom I can feel myself protected. I represent myself, that he will be sincere as a drop of water, the careful, good father and certainly the owner of the house. I very much hope to find such person who will love me. I shall give accordingly the same feelings and qualities.
